            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高市早苗勝選緩解財政憂慮 日元有望創15個月來最大單周漲幅\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q7wGjTapAnF_5eEMhZgiTw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/28d10570-060b-11f1-bfff-0fb8e11579e9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高市早苗勝選緩解財政憂慮 日元有望創15個月來最大單周漲幅</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E5%8B%9D%E9%81%B8%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E6%86%82%E6%85%AE-%E6%97%A5%E5%85%83%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E5%89%B515%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%AE%E5%91%A8%E6%BC%B2%E5%B9%85-104004088.html",
